    dc:description "Figure 97. Polylepis pallidistigma Bitter A flowers B lower leaf surface C upper leaf surface D stipule sheaths E leaves F flowering branch G inflorescence H bark. Scale bars: 3 mm (A); 1 cm (B, C); 2 cm (F) 5 mm (G). Photographs A, D-H E. G. Urquiaga Flores B, C W. Arque." ;
